messages.message: Hi all! We are making a multilingual benchmark dataset to measure how well long doc chat performs on different languages. If you have a document(s) in a different language, could you share them in the thread below? It would be super useful :pray:  Also if you have questions to ask the doc (in that language), you can put them in the thread as well.
Thanks for this! This is definitely gonna be a key differentiator for our product!! :lfg:

cc @Timo Meijrink since he’s started many threads in this channel using dutch docs
